## Features Explained

### Web Search (DuckDuckGo)
- **Advantage**: Free, no API key required, no rate limiting
- **Limitation**: Requires internet connection
- **Data**: Real-time web results

### Offline Wikipedia
- **Advantage**: Works without internet, fast responses
- **Limitation**: Static data (not real-time)
- **Data**: Local SQLite database

